      "containerId": "insight",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 92,
      "width": 1540,
      "height": 46,
      "text": "A deterministic parser extracts a schema-validated contract; LLM agents handle only the genuinely fuzzy translation\n(Tableau calculations \u2192 DAX, visual intent \u2192 Power BI visuals). GitHub search for this architecture returns 0 results \u2014 publicly novel.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
